{"tid":231082,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"射鵰我都係揀李亞鵬周迅版","createTime":"2017-05-05T19:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T14:16:04.000Z","uid":67347,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a35e8c08da2295e1f3fd0afff16f2676ca24ea40","tid":231082,"uid":67347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T19:16:23.000Z","msg":"個陣為左睇而轉台亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會太浮誇<br />\n周迅係把聲問題姐<br />\n都演到個種靈氣<br />\n洪7公黃藥師都揀角揀得好正<br />\n而家成日拍到偶像劇咁<br />\nd 景又要好唯美<br />\n接受唔到呢種方向<br />\n<br />\n我知翁美玲版係無敵<br />\n但確實未出世未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9592540f11e6f4aa9fe9dff0bb28016da09dd78a","tid":231082,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T19:19:48.000Z","msg":"而家普遍出面d人好多淨係話李一桐點靚點靚<br />\n但我淨係望到洪7公既造型已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b959abb5af3663a75ccc1a912f862983e47a55b9","tid":231082,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:39:57.000Z","msg":"翁美玲版其實唔係真係咁好，個角色改到好巴渣好野蠻咁，原著個蓉兒係好明白事理的。<br />\n<br />\n反而黃日華做郭靖仲出色，真人都有嗰種傻蠢戇嘅感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c659ffd73ea98443e280a6c6d33cb7c0c12c025","tid":231082,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翁美玲版其實唔係真係咁好，個角色改到好巴渣好野蠻咁，原著個蓉兒係好明白事理的。<br />\n<br />\n反而黃日華做郭靖仲出色，真人都有嗰種傻蠢戇嘅感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我揀呢套都係因為李亞鵬都有俾我咁既感覺<br />\n但我知有人話佢似弱智多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe77d740bb1d2d1f1a97017d233dec3b5a83020","tid":231082,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翁美玲版